<h3>Game Category Prescription</h3>
<ul class="s">
    <li class="n">To prescribe game category to patients based on the diagnosed medical/dementia condition:</li>
    <ol>
        <li>Press “Recommend Game Category” button and a list of game categories will appear.</li>
        <li>For each category that is to be prescribed, enter the following details</li>
        <ul>
            <li>Comments : Additional notes to take note of</li>
            <li>Duration (Minutes) : Amount of time (in minutes) a patient is prescribed to play the game category</li>
            <li>Days : Number of days the game category is prescribed to patient</li>
        </ul>
        <li>Press “Submit” button to prescribe or “Cancel” button to cancel option.</li>
    </ol>
    <br />
    <li class="n">To edit/un-prescribe a game category prescription:</li>
    <ol>
        <li>Press the “Edit” button under “Games Categories” section.</li>
        <li>Enter appropriate changes into the fields. To un-prescribe, click on the dropdown box under “Prescribed” column and select “No” option. Enter a reason for un-prescribing.</li>
        <li>Press “Submit” button to make changes or “Cancel” button to cancel option.</li>
    </ol>
</ul>


